@gaming_foodie's Korean Fried Shrimp will quickly become a favorite! Tender, succulent shrimp are deep-fried and coated in a gochujang/soy sauce mixture making this dish perfect for date night in! 
👉 Link in bio for recipe 
🤗 Featured on thefeedfeed.com/korean-food Feed, Edited by @misshangrypants

node.text:
Use @filippoberio_us for all of your baking needs (#ad)! Heart-healthy #FilippoBerio Olive Oil takes butter’s place, which is what’s traditionally used in pie dough, for these Balsamic, Blackberry, and Ricotta Hand Pies. The olive oil sub along with the use of #vegan ricotta cheese makes this a #dairyfree treat! The recipe makes 8 of the cutest personal pies, perfect for summer picnics and days outdoors.

👉Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/fb-handpies #feedfeed #oliveoil #hearthealthy #pie #feedfeed #blackberry #baking #smallbatch

Thanks to @chefwillcoleman for showing us how to make these Fried Pork Chop Sandwiches w/ Maple Peppercorn Aioli in commemoration of Juneteenth. Do yourself a big favor and pick up all the ingredients (recipes on our site are shoppable!) and make them this weekend.
👉Find the recipe at ff.recipes/pork-chop-sandwich
🤗Featured on thefeedfeed.com/juneteenth-recipes Feed, edited by @meikoandthedish
⭐️Keep tagging #feedfeed @thefeedfeed for a chance to be featured

node.text:
Is it safe to say Zucchini is having its own hot girl summer? 🧐 We're gonna say.... YES. Now that that's established, @lmsthompson recreated @taylorgolub's recipe for these Cheesy Zucchini Fritters! Grated zucchini is whipped up into a batter with labneh, cheese (she used feta), eggs, and bright oregano. And feel free to swap in an equal amount of your favorite gluten-free flour blend. Fry 'em up until golden brown and crisp and dish out all the summer vibes.
👉 Link in bio for recipe 
🤗 Featured on thefeedfeed.com/zucchini Feed
🌟 Keep tagging #feedfeed @thefeedfeed for a chance to be featured
.⁣
.⁣
.⁣
#zucchini #fritters #zucchinifritters #zucchinirecipes #summer #appetizer

node.text:
Whether you planted a windowsill herb garden, or have more herbs than you know what to do with, we’ve got ideas for using them up in our Weekly Meal Plan! We kick off the week with our take on @amywilichowski @tiktok famous pesto fried egg trend! We turned it into an egg sandwich with garlic toast and juicy summer tomatoes. It's our new favorite breakfast for dinner! 
👆 Get team Feedfeed's @clarelangan recipe in this week's Meal Planner + subscribe through the link in our profile.
🌟 Keep tagging #feedfeed @thefeedfeed for a chance to be featured
.⁣
.⁣
.⁣
